# install

* install pmbootstrap
* pmbootstrap init
* pmbootstrap install

# troubleshooting

* pmbootstrap update
* pmbootstrap -v install
* go to the [issues](https://github.com/postmarketOS/pmbootstrap/issues/) page
* pmbootstrap pkgrel_bump --auto

